---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import AppButtons from '../components/AppButtons.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Mee Foundation - Get the app">
  <Header
    backgroundColor="backdrop-blur-md"
    logoColor="blue"
    withoutProgress={true}
  />
  <main class="scrollContainer transform-gpu">
    <article
      class="relative flex h-full min-h-screen w-screen flex-col items-center justify-between gap-10 overflow-hidden pt-25 md:pt-36"
    >
      <div
        class="relative z-100 mb-25 flex h-auto w-screen max-w-2xl flex-1 flex-col items-center justify-center gap-10 md:mb-30"
      >
        <div class="bg-1"></div>
        <section
          class="section top-0 z-100 flex w-screen items-center justify-center mb-3.5"
        >
          <div
            class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 transition-opacity duration-500 md:p-0"
          >
            <div class="overflow-hidden">
              <h1
                class="marker mt-[28px] animate-riseIn text-3xl font-bold md:text-4xl lg:mt-[52px] lg:text-6xl"
              >
                The <mark>Mee app</mark>
              </h1>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        <section class="z-100 overflow-hidden">
          <h2
            class="text animate-riseIn px-6 text-center text-base leading-relaxed text-black/80 animation-delay-800 md:text-xl"
          >
            We are on our journey towards a big vision of a human-centered user
            experience for the internet.
          </h2>
        </section>
        <section class="z-100 overflow-hidden">
          <h2
            class="text animate-riseIn px-6 text-center text-base leading-relaxed text-black/80 animation-delay-800 md:text-xl"
          >
            Meanwhile, we built the experimental smartwallets, which support the
            following functions: signing in/up to apps/sites without passwords,
            retrieving user information from their Google Account, sending GPC
            signal to indicate user privacy preferences.
          </h2>
        </section>
        <AppButtons btnSize="normal" noDescription={true} class="z-100" />
      </div>
      <Footer mode="dark" withAppButtons={false} />
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>
<style>
  .bg-1 {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 150vw;
    border-top-left-radius: 50%;
    border-top-right-radius: 50%;
    top: 40%;
    height: 100vh;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to top,
      rgba(249, 200, 137, 0.4) 75%,
      rgba(249, 182, 137, 0.4) 100%
    );
    filter: blur(100px);
    transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0);
    z-index: 1;
  }
</style>

<script>
  window.onbeforeunload = function () {
    window.scrollTo(0, 0);
  };
</script>
